# Deployment Environment Variables

## Frontend (Vercel)

Create these environment variables in your Vercel project settings:

```
VITE_API_URL=https://video-downloader-production-e4fe.up.railway.app
```

**IMPORTANT**: Set Root Directory to `frontend` in Vercel project settings!

## Backend (Railway)

Create these environment variables in your Railway service settings:

```
FRONTEND_URL=https://video-downloader-jade.vercel.app
PYTHON_VERSION=3.11
```

## Current Deployment URLs

- **Frontend (Vercel)**: https://video-downloader-jade.vercel.app/
- **Backend (Railway)**: https://video-downloader-production-e4fe.up.railway.app/

**Note:** See VERCEL_DEPLOYMENT.md for complete Vercel setup instructions.
